{
  "stem": "543.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took her with me, you know, and-- and carry her back to where I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and a-- a day later-- so they took us all out out of that place and took us in blocks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They closed us up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The block was half the size.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see it 100 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't lay down-- no drink, no washroom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Neustadt-Glewe was the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is like, just beside it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's the-- it's not in different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think the whole complex is Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at the-- they said Neustadt-Glewe, but it was actually, I think, Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in the-- in that place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they closed us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- all the people were sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the people had diarrhea-- you know when you don't get food and you don't get water, no-- so everybody had [GERMAN], like diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You are full with sores.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had lice climbing all over us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was so sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then, we-- the next day, the SS fled.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had all the uniforms outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, the-- the people, in that-- in that little room, they heard the SS.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We made a hole in the wall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you opened up the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody what in-- in Auschwitz was-- I mean, there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first thing, you look for food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, everybody was starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they don't get food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were looking for the arsenals if there was food in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was climbing over each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, what's going on there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't go near it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I find some sugar on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I was picking up the sugar-- and if I had a old coat on.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
